Here´s my glass_war_reloaded .
I hope that all the bugs r fixed now ,skyboxes should work (tested with a friend)
if not so please tell me ...

This mappack isnt a real mappack, I thought it would be nice to have some randowm skyboxes to make the map look different, so i compiled it 5 times with 5 different skys. 

Normally i would say go and decompile it and put another sky in it , but not every1 knows ho to do that... thats y I let u choose from these and hope every player or admin will have his favorite map to play on.

40 players could be a bit to much but I dont think that any1 will put that on a 40 men server... 
This map may cause lagg on some machines, although i removed some glass.

Furthermore i put some extra things in this map as allways (look at the last screenshot for more info)... if u played my glasstrap map u will know what I mean ;).


HAVE FUN!...
